<ul class="sub-menu collapse" id="collapse50" aria-labelledby="heading50" data-parent="#mobileNavAccordion"> <li class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-65213"><a href="https://granta.com/about/">About Granta</a> <li class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-74173"><a href="/merchandise">Merchandise</a> <li class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-65214"><a href="/team">The Granta Team</a> <li class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-65217"><a href="https://granta.com/prizes/">Prizes</a> <li class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-65216"><a href="https://granta.com/events/">Events</a> <li class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-83493"><a href="/jobs/">Careers</a> <li class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-103354"><a href="https://granta.com/grantas-environmental-policy/">Grantas Environmental Policy</a></ul>
